title: Array

title: Function
definition: A function is a block of code that can be reused.

title: Object
definition: An object is a data structure that can store a collection of properties.

title: Variable

title: Python
definition: A high-level programming language known for its simplicity and readability.

title: List

title: Function
definition: A block of reusable code that performs a specific task.

title: Module

title: C#

title: Class

title: Inheritance
